== Xero

= Set up development application

Activate the Demo company from https://my.xero.com/!xkcD/Dashboard if needed.

Go to https://api.xero.com and login as matt@yoomee.com, key of XERO.

Go to My applications and add a new private application, linked to Demo Company. Upload the .cer from lib/xero/development/

Copy OAuth Credentials to development.yml

Win!